Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.56,Default,Shadow,0,0,0,,{TIME:247101,248560}Then keep your mouth shut.{NOTE:じゃあ黙ってなよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.31,0:04:13.64,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:251314,253649}Where are you going, Mad?{NOTE:どこ行くんだ、マッド。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.64,0:04:16.69,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:253649,256694}To collect Kinship Stones, of course.{NOTE:絆石狩りに決まってるでしょう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:19.07,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:256694,259071}You too, Gale?{NOTE:おめえもかよ、ゲイル？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.07,0:04:21.49,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:259071,261491}Yeah, something like that.{NOTE:まっ、そんな感じっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.49,0:04:23.15,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:261491,263159}Something like that?!{NOTE:感じって何だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:25.03,Default,Wrath,0,0,0,,{TIME:263159,265036}Huuuh!?{NOTE:ううう～っ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:30.41,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:266412,270416}I don't think the Ebon Riders will stay silent for too long after that.{NOTE:ブラックライダーズがこのまま黙っているとは思えません。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.41,0:04:35.67,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:270416,275671}Do you suppose they'll come to attack our village again?{NOTE:やつらがまたこの村を襲ってくるかもしれんということだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:39.42,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:275671,279425}Well, we did take back\Nall the Kinship Stones they stole.{NOTE:あいつらのとこにあった絆石取り返してきたからね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.67,0:04:43.26,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:280676,283262}I won't let anyone take it ever again.{NOTE:二度と手放さないぞ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:47.26,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:283262,287266}As far as I know, they were trying\Nto get some information out of Avinia, right?{NOTE:それにあいつらアユリアから何か聞き出そうとしてたんだろ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.43,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:287266,288434}Yes.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.81,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:288434,290812}Even though I made it clear I don't know anything…{NOTE:私が何も知らないと言っても…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.81,0:04:53.64,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:290812,293648}…they kept inquiring about a secret art of my village.{NOTE:…村の秘術を話せと言っていました。}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.64,0:04:55.94,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:293648,295942}About that secret art…{NOTE:アユリアの村の秘術って…}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.94,0:05:01.28,Default,Cheval,1,1,0,,{TIME:295942,301280}Does it have to do with a monument with an inscription:\N"The flying ones' crystals cannot become one"?{NOTE:…石碑にあった｢乗り人の結晶一つとならん｣ってやつ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.28,0:05:03.03,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:301280,303032}How do you know about that?{NOTE:どうしてそれを？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:05.28,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:303032,305284}We went to your village.{NOTE:俺たち村に行ったんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.28,0:05:07.20,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:305284,307203}I see…{NOTE:そうだったんですか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:11.04,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:307203,311040}But that's about all I know about it, too.{NOTE:でも秘術のことはそれだけなんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.04,0:05:14.54,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:311040,314544}They might want to try and kidnap Avinia again.{NOTE:あいつらまたアユリアをさらいに来るかもしれないな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.54,0:05:18.88,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:314544,318881}Probably. Which means we're going to have to\Nprepare proper countermeasures.{NOTE:だから俺たちも対抗策を用意した方がいいと思うんだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:20.50,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:318881,320508}Countermeasures?{NOTE:対抗策？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:24.47,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:320508,324470}Yes, as in, we're all going to have to get stronger to protect the village.{NOTE:簡単に言えば村全体で強くなるってこと。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:25.38,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:324470,325388}Ah…{NOTE:あ～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:27.59,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:325388,327598}You're right.{NOTE:そうだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:31.72,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:327598,331727}Nariki, is your Velocidrome your only Monstie?{NOTE:ナリキ、お前のオトモンドスランポスだけか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.72,0:05:34.48,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:331727,334480}Yeah, nothing's changed.{NOTE:はいっす。そうなんすよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:37.85,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:334480,337859}I'd like to bond with other Monsties, though.{NOTE:自分他のオトモンとも絆を結びたいっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:39.02,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:337859,339026}Good idea.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.69,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:339026,340695}The more, the better.{NOTE:増やした方がいいね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.69,0:05:41.86,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:340695,341863}Lute.{NOTE:リュート。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.03,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:341863,345032}I think I'll go learn the rite of channeling.{NOTE:私は伝承の儀を教わりに行こうと思います。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.03,0:05:46.90,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:345032,346909}At Dede Geezer's place?{NOTE:デデ爺のとこ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.49,0:05:50.74,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:347493,350746}I want to make Frostfang stronger.{NOTE:ヒョウガの能力をもっと目覚めさせたいんです。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:55.41,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:350746,355418}Well, if that's the case, I'd like to expand my Monstie's abilities, too.{NOTE:そういうことなら俺も行ってオトモンに能力を持たせたいな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.41,0:05:56.79,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:355418,356794}You mean Qurupeco?{NOTE:クルペッコに？}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.79,0:05:59.46,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:356794,359463}What's wrong with making Qurupeco stronger?{NOTE:クルペッコに持たせて何が悪い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.46,0:06:03.46,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:359463,363467}I'm gonna go search for Monstie eggs on Mount Celion!{NOTE:自分セリオン山にオトモンの卵を探しに行きたいっす。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.46,0:06:06.80,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:363467,366804}Mount Celion? Isn't that too much for just you and your Velocidrome?{NOTE:ドスランポスでセリオン山は無理なんじゃない？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.80,0:06:07.80,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:366804,367805}Huh?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.80,0:06:11.60,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:367805,371601}Well, it'll be fine if you come with me.{NOTE:先輩たちがついてきてくれれば大丈夫っすよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.56,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:371601,372560}Huh?{NOTE:はあ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.56,0:06:14.10,Default,Hyoro,0,0,0,,{TIME:372560,374103}We're going, too?{NOTE:僕たちも行くの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:14.93,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:374103,374937}All right!{NOTE:よし！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.43,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:374937,376439}I'll go with you as well.{NOTE:俺もそっちに行こう。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.77,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:376439,377773}With a Qurupeco?{NOTE:クルペッコで？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:19.73,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:377773,379734}What's wrong with Qurupecos?{NOTE:クルペッコで何が悪い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.73,0:06:23.61,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:379734,383613}Okay, then I'll take Avinia to Dede Geezer's place.{NOTE:じゃあ俺はアユリアをデデ爺のとこに連れていくから…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:26.24,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:383613,386240}So you guys take Nariki.{NOTE:…ナリキを誰か連れていってやって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.24,0:06:29.57,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:386240,389577}But, thinking back to the Ebon Riders' last attack…{NOTE:ブラックライダーズが襲ってきたときのことを考えて…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.91,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:389577,391913}…it'd be better if someone stayed here in the village.{NOTE:…村に誰かが残っていた方がいいよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:34.04,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:391913,394040}Okay then, Cheval, I'm counting on you.{NOTE:じゃあ、シュヴァル、頼むよ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:34.74,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:394040,394749}Huh…?{NOTE:えっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.00,0:06:37.71,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:396000,397710}Sure. I'll stay here.{NOTE:うん。分かった。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.71,0:06:40.50,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:397710,400504}If we divide Riders into three teams…{NOTE:ライダーを３つの隊に分けるなら…}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:43.42,Default,Omna,0,0,0,,{TIME:400504,403424}…your strength will be distributed accordingly.{NOTE:…それ相応に考えねばならんな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.42,0:06:44.34,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:403424,404342}All right!{NOTE:よーし！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.34,0:06:46.80,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:404342,406802}I hope you're all in top form!\NWe're departing soon!{NOTE:みんな、絶好調で出発だ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.13,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:406802,408137}On a Qurupeco?{NOTE:クルペッコで？}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:50.01,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:408137,410014}What do you have against my Qurupeco?{NOTE:クルペッコで何が悪い！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.30,0:06:53.93,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:412308,413935}All right then, we're going!{NOTE:じゃあ行ってくる！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.93,0:06:56.64,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:413935,416646}We'll find a nice egg for sure!{NOTE:いい卵を見つけてくるぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.85,Default,Cheval,0,0,0,,{TIME:416646,418856}Just leave the village to us.{NOTE:村のことは任せて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:01.73,Default,Mille,0,0,0,,{TIME:418856,421734}Why do I have to stay behind?{NOTE:何であたしが居残り組に…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:03.65,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:421734,423653}Lute, Navi.{NOTE:リュート、ナビちゃん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:06.82,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:423653,426822}I made you a lot of my special Energy Drinks.{NOTE:これ元気ドリンコとか色々入ってるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.49,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:426822,428491}Energy Drinks!?{NOTE:元気ドリンコ!?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.49,0:07:10.82,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:428491,430826}Better give them to Nariki!{NOTE:それはナリキたちに持たせてやれ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.82,0:07:14.28,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:430826,434288}Don't worry, there's enough for everyone!{NOTE:大丈夫。みんなの分ちゃんとあるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:17.04,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:434288,437041}I-I see… hehe…{NOTE:そ、そうか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:20.62,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:437041,440628}Lute, I'm going back to the Scriveners' headquarters.{NOTE:リュート。私書士隊本部に戻るけど…}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:23.00,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:440628,443005}If you need help, you can ask me anytime.{NOTE:…何かあったらいつでも相談してね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.00,0:07:23.83,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:443005,443839}Sure.{NOTE:うん。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.80,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:443839,446801}I'll drop by if I need anything, Lilia.{NOTE:そのときは頼むよ、リリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:28.63,Default,Lilia,0,0,0,,{TIME:446801,448636}Great.{NOTE:任せて。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.47,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:451931,455476}It's good that we get to take\Nthe main road to the Darj Snowfields.{NOTE:今回は街道を通ってタルジュ雪原に行くのだな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.39,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:455476,457395}Yeah. We couldn't afford to last time.{NOTE:前のときよりは余裕だな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.02,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:462817,465027}Calm down, Fool.{NOTE:落ち着きなさい、フール。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.02,0:07:48.40,Default,Mad,0,0,0,,{TIME:465027,468406}I know they're mostly small pickings,\Nbut they have strength in their numbers.{NOTE:雑魚が交じっているとはいえあの頭数です。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.99,Default,Nuts,0,0,0,,{TIME:469782,472994}Master Gale, aren't we going to hunt for Kinship Stones, too?{NOTE:ゲイルさまも絆石狙いなんですか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.99,0:07:55.83,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:472994,475830}I'll leave it to Mad this time.{NOTE:そっちはマッドの兄貴に任せるか。}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:07:57.41,Default,Gale,0,0,0,,{TIME:475830,477415}My goal is different.{NOTE:俺の狙いは別だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:05.25,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:483504,485256}As usual, it's freezing here.{NOTE:相変わらず寒い、寒い。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.50,0:08:08.80,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:486507,488801}Mount Celion is in that direction.{NOTE:セリオン山はあっちの方だ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.80,0:08:12.13,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:488801,492138}We're headed to the Darj Snowfields,\Nso this is where we have to split.{NOTE:俺たちはタルジュの山小屋に行くから、ここでお別れだ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.84,0:08:14.51,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:492847,494515}Be careful!{NOTE:気を付けるのだぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:16.10,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:494515,496100}You too.{NOTE:しっかりね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.10,0:08:18.81,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:496100,498811}I'll be there with them, so it'll be okay!{NOTE:俺がいるんだ。任せとけ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.02,Default,Spex,0,0,0,,{TIME:498811,501022}Okay then, we're going!{NOTE:じゃあ、行ってくるから。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:23.23,Default,Lute,0,0,0,,{TIME:501022,503232}Let's go, Avinia.{NOTE:行こう。アユリア。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.23,0:08:24.44,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:503232,504442}Okay.{NOTE:はい。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.11,0:08:31.24,Default,Nariki,0,0,0,,{TIME:509113,511240}Being able to fly sure is nice…{NOTE:飛べるっていいっすよね～。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:33.99,Default,Beats,0,0,0,,{TIME:511240,513993}Are you going to aim for a flying Monstie?{NOTE:そういうのオトモンにするか？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.99,0:08:36.78,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:513993,516787}We'll just have to see what we can find.{NOTE:何が見つかるかは行ってみないとな。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.78,0:08:39.04,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:516787,519040}All right then, let's go.{NOTE:さあ、俺たちも行くぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.04,0:08:41.20,Default,Dan,0,0,0,,{TIME:519040,521208}In top form!{NOTE:絶好調！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.50,Default,Navirou,0,0,0,,{TIME:527173,528507}I can see it!{NOTE:見えてきたぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.50,0:08:50.42,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:528507,530426}There's the Darj cottage.{NOTE:タルジュの山小屋ね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:54.34,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:530426,534346}So Kuang village's legend was right.{NOTE:やっぱりクアン村の言い伝えは正しかったんだわ。}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.34,0:08:55.97,Default,Fifi,0,0,0,,{TIME:534346,535973}What was it about?{NOTE:何のこと？}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:09:00.81,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:535973,540811}That a Wyverian living in the snowy mountains\Ncan awaken monsters' powers.{NOTE:雪山の竜人はモンスターの力を目覚めさせるって。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.64,0:09:04.27,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:541645,544273}Here you are again.{NOTE:また来たなおめえら。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.27,0:09:06.40,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:544273,546400}Long time no see, mister.{NOTE:お久しぶりです。おじさま。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:10.78,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:546400,550780}Looks like you enjoy more than just riddles.{NOTE:おじさまはやはりただのなぞなぞ好きの人ではなかったんですね。}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.82,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:550780,552823}Someone who can "gargau"…?{NOTE:ガルガルと鳴く…}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.86,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:552823,553866}Huh?{NOTE:あっ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.86,0:09:17.78,Default,Riddlemaster,0,0,0,,{TIME:553866,557787}Which Monstie can "gargau" after being rearranged?{NOTE:入れ替えるとガルガル鳴くモンスターはな～んダ？}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.78,0:09:19.91,Default,Avinia,0,0,0,,{TIME:557787,559914}"Gargau"…?{NOTE:えっ…ガルガル？}
